  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Weapon Research: Fighter/Bombers and Missiles<o:p></=
o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Napoar</span> were long ago=
 a race
  of humanoid aliens. Before <span class=3DGramE>being a space-faring race<=
/span>
  they were able to foresee a massive climate changing event to their home
  world. The <span class=3DSpellE>Napoar</span> had not developed the abili=
ty to
  travel between the stars, instead they were able to progress their techno=
logy
  so far that they were able to transfer their consciousness in to cybernet=
ic
  bodies.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Napoar</span> developed bod=
ies were
  extremely hardy and able to withstand extreme heat and weather to survive=
 the
  massive change to their home world.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>In transcending to this synthetic <span class=3DGram=
E>state</span>
  the <span class=3DSpellE>Napoar</span> lost many of the evolution develop=
ed
  emotional instinctual behaviors. They were no longer driven by a will to =
seek
  power and have lost their aggression.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Napoar</span> find non aggr=
essive
  races to be far more agreeable and seek for every race in the Galaxy to f=
ind
  their own place and to coexist and help each other survive. They see no
  reason why war or conflict is needed at all.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>In game terms this race can be one of the fastest to
  spread to other planets. Because of their new bodies they find it easy to
  develop the technology to populate different types of worlds. They are
  extremely passive though and are not the best at war. They will attempt to
  live in coexistence with other peaceful races.</p>
